'''西班牙裔美国人'''（{{lang-en|Spanish Americans}}；{{lang-es|españoles-americanos}}、{{lang|es|norteamericanos de origen español}}、{{lang|es|estadounidenses de origen español}}）是来自欧洲国家西班牙的美国人。<ref>Most dictionaries give this definition as the first or only definition for "Spanish American". ''The American Heritage Dictionary of the English Language'' (3rd ed.) (1992). Boston: Houghton Mifflin. ISBN 0-395-44895-6. ''Merriam-Webster's Collegiate Dictionary'' (11th ed.) (2003). Springfield: Merriam-Webster. ISBN 0-87779-807-9. ''The Random House Dictionary of the English Language'' (2nd ed.) (1987). New York: Random House. ISBN 0-394-50050-4. ''Shorter Oxford English Dictionary on Historical Principles'' (2007). New York: Oxford University Press. ISBN 978-0-19-920687-2. ''Webster's New Dictionary and Thesaurus'' (2002). Cleveland: Wiley Publishing. ISBN 978-0-471-79932-0</ref>1565年以来，西班牙裔美国人大量出现在美国佛罗里达州，现在是美国第八大族群。<ref name=loc>{{cite web |url=http://www.americaslibrary.gov/jb/colonial/jb_colonial_augustin_1.html |title=A Spanish Expedition Established St. Augustine in Florida |publisher=[[Library_of_Congress|Library of Congress]] |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2002-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20020911221037/http://www.americaslibrary.gov/jb/colonial/jb_colonial_augustin_1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>大约有5000万美国人是拉美裔，大多数主要有西班牙血统，族群如此庞大，西班牙殖民主义曾在墨西哥和南美（巴西除外）建立殖民地是主要原因。

